text: Quarantined here during the pandemic. Good water pressure. Clean and comfy, however, you can hear a lot of loud banging from far away and internet reception isn't the best.
single rooms are better here, for twin sharing go for gh2
Fair and safe space, plus basic furniture for about 500 sgd(2016). Water pressure is not very stable.

Peaceful ambience. Nice place to stay.
(Lived there for 1 year)
Amazing memories. Big rooms compared to GH2. Miss this place
